    public class QueuePhPh2
extends GeomProcess<examples.jmarkov.QueuePhPh2State,examples.jmarkov.QueuePhPh2Event>
    This class implements a system whit two tandem servers each one with a phase service. The first server has an infinite capacity and the second server has finite capacity.
    Author:
    Julio Goez. Universidad de los Andes.
